{"tid":923494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暗黑郭雪芙宣布引退！ 宅宅崩潰怒吼「去你的2018」","createTime":"2018-12-01T09:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T03:26:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"29f82db11633c327c46ef880309179b5ac3a4818","tid":923494,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"28歲日本AV女優水野朝陽長相甜美，擁有G罩杯姣好身材，加上招牌短髮，受封「暗黑郭雪芙」，她出道將滿6週年，昨（30）突然宣布引退，讓粉絲崩潰不已。<br />\n <br />\n水野朝陽30日在推特表示，去年此時做出引退決定，手邊的工作會在2月底前完成，她提到2月出道屆滿6週年，是個引退的好時機，接下來會朝新的目標邁進，粉絲得知後，紛紛哀號「悲報呀呀呀！」、「今年最難過的消息」、「淫河又殞落一顆淫星」、「為什麼這麼多女優今年退休，去你的2018」、「崩潰！！！」"},{"pid":"f56889326f034281293256a514a080287540ad98","tid":923494,"uid":204306,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd25c9de3b5080269bc99f1378c9e9d843e9a5cf","tid":923494,"uid":39365,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"水野我至愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1be02d462c21bf400a843cd267e957768dd6cc8","tid":923494,"uid":132038,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9ca4b124308b279c9bdf6b050912ba9937f6bea","tid":923494,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"大肚呀⋯⋯"},{"pid":"9c431b66dc36ee35efdd03262be2df4f0ac0b3d9","tid":923494,"uid":2661,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"水野朝陽好好j 點解要引退<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1e43f2dea08833f4dd15946f52be81482a6797","tid":923494,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime